u \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|''[[Mitron]]'' \n|\"Sawarne Lage\"\n|Jubin Nautiyal \n|rowspan=\"3\"|Tanishk Bagchi\n|\n|-\n|\"Sawarne Lage (Female Version)\"\n|[[Nikhita Gandhi]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Chalte Chalte\" (Remake)\n|Atif Aslam\n|\n|-\n|\"Sanedo\"\n|[[Darshan Raval]], [[Raja Hasan]]\n|Tanishk Bagchi, Vayu\n|along with Vayu\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|''[[Loveyatri]]''\n|\"Akh Lad Jaave\"\n|Jubin Nautiyal, Asees Kaur, Badshah \n|Badshah, Tanishk Bagchi\n|\n|-\n|\"Rangtaari\"\n|[[Dev Negi]], Raja Hasan, [[Yo Yo Honey Singh]]\n|Shabbir Ahmed, Yo Yo Honey Singh and Hommie Dilliwala\n|\n|-\n|\"Tera Hua\"\n|[[Atif Aslam]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Manoj Muntashir, Arafat Mehmood, Shabbir Ahmed\n|\n|-\n|\"Tera Hua (Unplugged)\"\n|Atif Aslam, Asees Kaur\n|\n|-\n|\"Dholida\"\n|Udit Narayan, [[Palak Muchhal]], Neha Kakkar, Raja Hasan\n|Shabbir Ahmed \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Jalebi (film)|Jalebi]]'' \n|\"Tera Mera Rishta (Duet)\"\n|[[KK (singer)|KK]], Shreya Ghoshal\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Arafat Mehmood\n|\n|-\n|\"Tera Mera Rishta (Male)\"\n|KK \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Badhaai Ho]]''\n|\"Badhaiyan Tenu\"\n|Brijesh Shandilya, Romi, Jordan\n|Vayu\n|\n|-\n|\"Morni Banke\" (Remake)\n|[[Guru Randhawa]], Neha Kakkar\n|MellowD\n|\n|-\n|''[[Baazaar]]''\n|\"Kem Cho\"\n|[[Jyotica Tangri]], Ikka \n|Shabbir Ahmed, Ikka \n|\n|-\n|''[[K.G.F: Chapter 1]]''\n|\"Gali Gali Mein Phirta Hai (Remake)\"\n|Neha Kakkar\n|[[Anand Bakshi]], [[Rashmi Virag]]\n|Kannada film (Hindi Dubbed)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Zero (2018 film)|Zero]]''\n|\"Heer Badnaam \"\n|Romy\n|[[Kumaar]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Tanha Hua (Remake)\"\n|[[Nooran Sisters|Jyoti Nooran]], Rahat Fateh Ali Khan\n|Irshad Kamil\n|\n|-\n|\"Dama Dum Mast (Remake)\"\n|Altamash Faridi\n|Traditional \n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|''[[Simmba]]''\n|\"Tere Bin\" (Remake)\n|Rahat Fateh Ali Khan, Asees Kaur\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Rashmi Virag\n|\n|-\n|\"Bandeya Re Bandeya\"\n|[[Arijit Singh]], Asees Kaur, Altamash Faridi\n|\n|-\n|\"[[Aankh Maarey]] (Remake)\"\n|[[Mika Singh]], Neha Kakkar, [[Kumar Sa