]]''\n|\"Nachan Nu Jee Karda\" (Remake)\n|Romy, Nikhita Gandhi \n|\n|-\n|style=\"background:#ffc\"|''[[Sooryavanshi]]''\n|\"Tip Tip Barsa Paani (Remake)\"\n|TBA\n|\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=3|''[[Satyameva Jayate 2]]''\n|\"Door Se Paas (Remake)\"\n|[[B Praak]], [[Neeti Mohan]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Kabhi Aar Kabhi Paar (Remake)\"\n|[[Jubin Nautiyal]], Tulsi Kumar\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Bum Bum Tam Tam (Remake)\"\n|[[MC Fioti]], [[Badshah (rapper)|Badshah]], [[Harrdy Sandhu]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|style=\"background:#ffc;\"|''[[Dostana 2]]''\n|\"Maa Da Laadla 2.0.\"(Remake)\n|[[Master Saleem]], [[Guru Randhawa]], [[Sunidhi Chauhan]], [[Badshah (rapper)|Badshah]]\n|\n|\n|}\n\n===Albums / Singles===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#cfc; text-align:center;\"\n| '''Year'''\n| '''Album(s)/Single(s)'''\n| '''Song'''\n| '''Singer(s)/Co-Singer(s)'''\n| '''Lyrics'''\n| '''Note'''\n|-\n|2013\n|''Paisa Tu Hai Kameeni Cheez''\n| \"Paisa Tu Hai Kameeni Cheez\"\n|Tanishk Bagchi\n|Alaukik Rahi\n|First single\n|-\n|2018\n|''Leja Re''\n| \"Leja Re\"\n|[[Dhvani Bhanushali]]\n|[[Rashmi Virag]]\n|Remake\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|2019\n|''Vaaste''\n| \"Vaaste\"\n|[[Dhvani Bhanushali]], [[Nikhil D'Souza]]\n|Arafat Mehmood\n|\n|-\n|''Khud Se Zyada''\n| \"Khud Se Zyada\"\n|Tanishk Bagchi, Zara Khan\n|Tanishk Bagchi\n|\n|-\n|''Choodiyan''\n| \"Choodiyan\"\n|[[Asees Kaur]], [[Dev Negi]]\n|[[Shabbir Ahmed (lyricist)|Shabbir Ahmed]]\n|\n|-\n|''Nai Jaana''\n| \"Nai Jaana\"\n|[[Tulsi Kumar]], [[Sachet-Parampara|Sachet Tandon]]\n|Nirmaan\n|Remake\n|-\n|''Maaserati''\n| \"Maaserati\"\n| Tanishk Bagchi, Vayu, Akasa\n|Vayu\n|\n|-\n|''Yaad Piya Ki Aane Lagi''\n| \"Yaad Piya Ki Aane Lagi\"\n|[[Neha Kakkar]]\n|[[Jaani (songwriter)|Jaani]]\n|Remake\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|2020\n| ''Mere Angne Mein''\n| \" Mere Angne Mein\"\n| [[Neha Kakkar]] ,[[Raja Hasan]]\n| Vayu\n|Remake\n|-\n| ''Swag Se Solo'' ft.[[Salman Khan]]\n| \" Swag Se Solo\"\n| [[Sachet-Parampara|Sachet Tandon]], Tanishk Bagchi\n| Vayu\n| Along with Vayu, Pepsi Ad